item.title: CodeChef Interview Experience
item.description: I’m a regular user at LinkedIn and I came across the Software Development Engineer Internship’s poster by CodeChef when I was browsing through the feed one day. CodeChef’s interview process is very different unlike most other companies including its parent Directi. Due to COVID-19, my whole interview process was virtual. Online Coding Round at CodeChef – 3 hours 1st and 2nd question were of beginner level (Reference) 3rd question (Easy) – You are given an array A1,A2,.
